name: mixed_nrmh54
source:
def mixed_nrmh54(x, y):
    t1 = jnp.abs(x)
    t2 = t1 + y
    t3 = jnp.mean(t2)
    return t3
jaxpr:
{ lambda ; a:f32[2,4] b:f32[2,4]. let
    c:f32[2,4] = abs a
    d:f32[2,4] = add c b
    e:f32[] = reduce_sum[axes=(0, 1) out_sharding=None] d
    f:f32[] = div e 8.0:f32[]
  in (f,) }
